// Local Development Configuration (optional override)
// Copy this file to Local.xcconfig to override DEVELOPMENT_TEAM locally.
// Local.xcconfig is gitignored. The project uses Default.xcconfig for CI and default team.

// Your Apple Developer Team ID
// Find it at: https://developer.apple.com/account → Membership → Team ID
// Or in Xcode: Preferences → Accounts → Select team → View Details
DEVELOPMENT_TEAM = YOUR_TEAM_ID_HERE
